title: Contemporary Instrumentals Collection
description: This is a collection of contemporary jazz and new age music from the 1980s and 1990s. There are two files, one labeled 1980s and the other, labeled 1990s and they each have two disc files that contain songs from compilations that I've created: The Contemporary Instrumentals Collection, Vol. 1: The 1980s and The Contemporary Instrumentals Collection, Vol. 2: The 1990s. The set features artists such as The Rippingtons, Suzanne Ciani, Michael Gettel, Fattburger, and many more. Also the songs featured in this collection are a tribute to the Music Choice channel, "Contemporary Instrumentals", a channel that is only available in limited areas (I once had it on my TV for a year before the signal dropped). Anyway, I hope you enjoy the music
